commit message:
first experimental version for reading SIM card using OMAPI
(Open Mobile API), also includes a Xposed module to override OMAPI security rules
fox crash on devices without OMAPI, return correct SW when AID not found

changed min API level to 19 (KITKAT), use reader mode instead of foreground dispatch,
so we can also read other phones which use card-emulation without getting Android Beam in the way
added strings, don't try to read CLPC and NFC infos when using OMAPI
send some more GET DATA commands
cleanup, also did some tests with other AIDs
